title: 726: THIS BITCOIN FRACTAL COULD DRIVE PRICE TO $390,000 THIS BULL CYCLE PEAK!! BTC FUTURES ETF LAUNCH!!
description:
Bitcoin has broken the $60K level and is back in the area of its all-time high (ATH) set in April 2021. Based on a fractal analysis of charts of previous BTC cycles, the peak prediction for the ongoing bull market even reaches the vicinity of $390K.

Bitcoin market analyst, TechDev has tweeted a series of charts on the possibility of future long-term movement of BTC.
